<plot>Black blue-collar worker Mike Harris moves with his five children--David, Tommy, J.P., Liz and Richard--from Detroit to Los Angeles after the death of his wife to begin brand new lives. In L.A., Mike joins Harry, a white man, in opening a garage, and struggles to raise a family as a single parent in a lower-middle-class neighborhood.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?230794</url></doc>
